{"word":"ἐπαράομαι","slug":"ἐπαράομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπαράομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-άσομαι</el>) (ionic <el>-ήσομαι</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-ήρᾱμαι</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>:— <i>to imprecate curses upon</i>, <el>τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>ἐπ. λόγον</el> <i>to utter an imprecation</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}